snippet.title: Pythagorus' Theorum - Math Lesson 3,4,5 triangle
snippet.description: This math lesson looks at pythagorean math - how to work out the unknown sides of right angles triangle.  The 3,4,5 triangle will also be explored.  Become a math genius! To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
